OOC: Give me a break, willyas?  I'm having severe technical 
difficulties.

Empath ignites her jets to catch up with the group.  As she shoots 
skyward, she is about to thank the Matrix she's free of her 
cumbersome companions for the moment when she senses something ... 
odd.  She can think of no other word.  It is as if many voices were 
whispering at once in some unknown language.

Reaching out with her mind, she touches her leader's thoughts: <Lord 
Galvatron, I have found something rather unusual.  It may be another 
telepathic being.  Shall I investigate?>
